Maple Window and Eaves Cleaning is a professional Windows and Eaves Cleaning company that services the GTA and surrounding areas. Our services include:

    Window Cleaning
    Eavestrough Cleaning
    Eavestrough Repairs
    Pressure Washing
    and more

We specialize in high-end delicate work, and are dedicated to providing superior customer satisfaction that will leave even our most demanding customers satisfied. Our company is insured with the WSIB (Workplace Safety and Insurance Board) and has full liability insurance that covers you in the event of any accident, whether to a worker, your home or you. At Maple Window and Eaves Cleaning safety is, and always will be our main priority, but in case of an accident you can be assured that we are completely insured. Whether you need residential or commercial services, big or small, call or email Maple Window and Eaves Cleaning, and start seeing the difference today!
